    <p class="description">A plain-text file at <code>yoursite.com/robots.txt</code> that tells search engine crawlers which pages they can access. Misuse it and you can <strong>block your entire site from Google</strong> — but used correctly it protects crawl budget and keeps junk pages out of indexing queues.</p>
